panels.name: Allowed Received Bytes Outlier
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CiscoSourcefire
| parse "InitiatorBytes: *," as InitiatorBytes nodrop
| parse "ResponderBytes: *," as ResponderBytes nodrop
| parse "IngressInterface: *," as IngressInterface nodrop
| parse "Policy: *," as policy nodrop
| parse "URL: *" as url nodrop
| parse "DstIP: *," as dstip nodrop
| parse "SrcIP: *," as srcip nodrop
| parse "WebApplication: *," as WebApplication nodrop
| parse "AccessControlRuleAction: *," as accessControlRuleAction
| where accessControlRuleAction matches "Allow"
| timeslice 1m
| sum(ResponderBytes) as ResponderBytes by _timeslice
| outlier ResponderBytes

panels.name: Allowed Potential Threats
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CiscoSourcefire
[subquery: _view=threat_intel_ip_address
| compose ip_address keywords]
| parse "UserName: *," as UserName nodrop
| parse "DstPort: *," as DstPort nodrop
| parse "SrcPort: *," as SrcPort nodrop
| parse "Policy: *," as policy nodrop
| parse "URL: *" as url nodrop
| parse "DstIP: *," as dstip nodrop
| parse "SrcIP: *," as srcip nodrop
| parse "WebApplication: *," as WebApplication nodrop
| parse "AccessControlRuleAction: *," as accessControlRuleAction
| where accessControlRuleAction matches "Allow"
| lookup type, actor, raw, threatlevel as malicious_confidence from sumo://threat/cs on threat=dstip
| where !isBlank(raw)
| if (isEmpty(actor), "Unassigned", actor) as Actor
| parse field=raw "\"ip_address_types\":[\"*\"]" as ip_address_types nodrop
| parse field=raw "\"kill_chains\":[\"*\"]" as kill_chains nodrop  
| timeslice 1m
| count as threats by _timeslice, srcip, srcport, dstip, dstport, username, malicious_confidence, actor, kill_chains, ip_address_types
| sort _timeslice

panels.name: Top 25 Blocked URLs
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CiscoSourcefire
| parse "Policy: *," as policy nodrop
| parse "URL: *" as url nodrop
| parse "DstIP: *," as dstip nodrop
| parse "SrcIP: *," as srcip nodrop
| parse "WebApplication: *," as WebApplication nodrop
| parse "AccessControlRuleAction: *," as accessControlRuleAction
| where accessControlRuleAction matches "Block" and !isBlank(url)
| where url matches "*"
| timeslice 1m
| count as blocks by url
| sort blocks
| limit 25

panels.name: Sourcefire Blocked Traffic Pct Outlier
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CiscoSourcefire
| parse "AccessControlRuleAction: *," as accessControlRuleAction
| if(accessControlRuleAction matches "Block", 1, 0) as blocked
| timeslice 1m
| sum(blocked) as blocks, count(*) as total by _timeslice
| (blocks / total) * 100 as block_pct
| outlier block_pct window=10, threshold=5, consecutive=1, direction=+-
